OL,4,CGrants to buy electric cars to be cut
OL,5,Cto #2,500
OL,6, The government is to cut grants aimed
OL,7, at encouraging people to buy electric
OL,8, vehicles in a move that has been
OL,9, criticised by the motor industry.
OL,11,FThe Department for Transport will
OL,12,Freduce the grant from #3,000 to #2,500
OL,13,Fand restrict it to cars under #35,000.
OL,15,FBut Society of Motor Manufacturers and
OL,16,FTraders (SMMT) said it is "the wrong
OL,17,Fmove at the wrong time".
OL,19,FIt said the decision goes against the
OL,20,Fgovernment's zero emissions ambitions.
